title: Brendan Steele leads Fry.com Open, Justin Rose, Rory McIlroy in contention
text:
Brendan Steele leads Fry.com Open, Justin Rose, Rory McIlroy in contention Â© Getty Images Brendan Steele leads by one stroke after shooting a first-round 63 at the Frys.com Open in Napa. Filed:   23:13   23:13 UK 
Brendan Steele carded a nine-under-par 63 to earn a one-stroke lead on day one of the Frys.com Open in Napa. 
The American enjoyed a bogey-free opening round in California, sinking nine birdies in total to sit one shot clear of Venezeulan Jhonattan Vegas . 
Harold Varner III finished Thursday's session on seven-under, one stroke clear of Justin Thomas and D.H Lee after the pair shot a first-round 66 apiece. 
England's Justin Rose is four off the pace, with the former US Open champion a shot ahead of world number three Rory McIlroy on four-under.
